{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Story Synopsis</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>For centuries, humans have left Earth to seek new homes beyond the stars. Only a few remain on Earth to look after this slightly worn-out abode.<br></li><li>As facilities and services on Earth gradually cease, the once convenient life becomes more troublesome. Yet those who choose to stay enjoy this &quot;trouble.&quot;<br></li><li>Zhang Jun is among the few who returned to Earth from Utopia. Living in the mobile home &quot;Bamboo Basket&quot; with his brother Mu Feng and the robot butler Betsy.<br></li><li>One day, returning from work at the Dai Mountain Forest, Zhang Jun encounters Bai Fujiu, a messenger sent by Oz.<br></li><li>Bai Fujiu brings an upgrade report for the mechanical butler Betsy, disrupting the tranquility. This report makes their leisurely life suddenly interesting...<br></li><li>Here, there's no punk, no wasteland, no destruction or cruelty, not even intense contradictions or clashes of values. Just a peaceful and somewhat lazy life in the future world.<br></li><li>We invite you to enjoy this romantically leisurely electronic storyboard that heals the soul.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The entire game is composed of 800 sets of CGs, telling the story in a full-CG style.<br></li><li>True 4K resolution for meticulous detail.<br></li><li>Full voice acting with intricate sound effects and moving music.<br></li><li>A completely independent world view and timeline.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main Voice Actors</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Zhang Jun: Luttefair<br></li><li>Mu Feng: Wang Xinyu<br></li><li>Betsy: Xiange<br></li><li>Bai Fujiu: Z Jun<br></li><li>Broadcaster: Wang Xinyu<br></li><li>Hank: Wang Xinyu<br></li><li>Repair Bot: Wang Xinyu<br></li><li>Ms. Griffths: Long Shisan</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Music</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gustav Yu</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Hoo Hoo Hoo!!!","path":"ht